Package: authenticity
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, apache2.2-common, libapache2-mod-python, python-genshi (>= 0.5), python-ldap, python-openid, python-zope.interface
XB-Python-Version: ${python:Versions}
Description: OpenID Provider running on mod_python and using a LDAP directory
 Authenticity is a highly configurable OpenID Provider (also called a Server)
 which runs under Apache's mod_python. It supports OpenID 1.0, 1.1 and 2.0,
 does not rely on any particular LDAP schema and its appearance can be easily
 customized through templates.
